  ${APP_CMD} containers <name>
  ${APP_CMD} cbatch <name> [container]
  ${APP_CMD} run <name|all> [--parallel] -- <command>
  ${APP_CMD} update [name|all] [--parallel]
  ${APP_CMD} upgrade [name|all] [--parallel]
  ${APP_CMD} reboot [name|all]
  ${APP_CMD} copy-key <name>
  ${APP_CMD} validate
  ${APP_CMD} version
  ${APP_CMD} menu
  ${APP_CMD} help

命令说明:
  list              查看服务器列表
